-- New York City Marathon Will Go On as Scheduled, Bloomberg Says
-- B y   M i c h a e l   B u t e a u
-- 2012-10-31T19:19:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-31/new-york-city-marathon-will-go-on-as-scheduled-bloomberg-says.html
The  New York  City Marathon will be
held as scheduled on Nov. 4 as the city deals with the aftermath
of Hurricane Sandy, Mayor Michael Bloomberg said today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
